# AgToosa Review Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-review` or any review work, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Review.md` precisely.

## Key constraints

- All 4 specialist personas (Security Officer, Engineering Manager, CEO/PO, QA Lead) must complete before shipping.
- Any 🔴 Critical finding blocks the ship — do not proceed to `/agtoosa-ship` until all are resolved.
- The Simplifier pass is not optional — always refactor the top 3 complex sections.
- Apply the Iron Law root-cause protocol for every failing test or bug found during review.
- Update `Docs/Master-Plan.md` with review status after each run.
